"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/795887","Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","false","2017-12-06","<p>No assessment has been undertaken on land prices.</p><p> </p>","Suffolk Coastal","Dr Thérèse Coffey",,"2017-12-06T09:57:32.29Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/795887/answer","Biography information for Dr Thérèse  Coffey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/795887/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/795887/answer",,,,,"13","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","2017-11-28","Land: Prices","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs, what assessment he has made of the likely effect of the UK leaving the EU on land prices in rural communities.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre Brock","116213"
